# Chatbot Application with PDF Integration

## Overview

This project is a chatbot application that leverages a LLaMA-2 model to interact with users. It uses a Flask backend and a React frontend. The chatbot can process information from PDF documents and stores chat history in a MySQL database.

## Setup and Installation

### 1. Download the Model

Download the pre-trained model from the following link and place it in the `model` directory:

- [LLaMA-2 7B Chat Model](https://huggingface.co/TheBloke/Llama-2-7B-Chat-GGML/resolve/main/llama-2-7b-chat.ggmlv3.q8_0.bin)

### 2. Set Up the Virtual Environment

Create and activate a virtual Python environment:

```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use `venv\Scripts\activate`
